<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 02:15:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>有数百万种加密代币。几乎没有任何价值</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-06/there-are-millions-of-crypto-tokens-almost-none-have-any-value</link><description>查尔斯·霍斯金森很生气。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ikEKVt3kcQkU/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-06/there-are-millions-of-crypto-tokens-almost-none-have-any-value</guid></item><item><title>自 2024 年特朗普获胜以来，比特币首次跌破 60,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/bitcoin-falls-below-60-000-for-first-time-since-2024-trump-win</link><description>比特币自 2024 年 10 月以来首次跌破 60,000 美元，从美国总统唐纳德·特朗普连任后的市场宠儿转变为快速变化的投机格局的牺牲品。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iut13rHAsVz0/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 16:15:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/bitcoin-falls-below-60-000-for-first-time-since-2024-trump-win</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院主要委员会正在准备立法以制定加密货币税收结构</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-04/key-us-house-committee-preparing-legislation-to-forge-crypto-tax-structure</link><description>负责税收政策的众议院小组正在准备立法，赋予加密货币持有者在报告投资收益方面更大的灵活性，这对数字资产行业来说是一个潜在的福音。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQWwstahc5G8/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 23:58:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-04/key-us-house-committee-preparing-legislation-to-forge-crypto-tax-structure</guid></item><item><title>随着比特币接近特朗普之前的低点，加密货币暴跌加剧</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/ether-and-privacy-coins-lead-latest-losses-as-crypto-plummets</link><description>比特币周五下跌多达 5%，因为这种原始加密货币面临一波持续的抛售压力，接近美国总统唐纳德·特朗普赢得连任之前以来的最低点。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJcA.uTjm7M8/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 07:29:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/ether-and-privacy-coins-lead-latest-losses-as-crypto-plummets</guid></item><item><title>币安关系推动特朗普家族的稳定币财富</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/trump-family-s-stablecoin-wealth-fueled-by-binance-relationship</link><description>特朗普家族的一家加密货币企业通过进军稳定币获得了丰厚的利润，部分归功于与币安控股有限公司的促销安排。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iVKkNc9k1_tQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 12:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/trump-family-s-stablecoin-wealth-fueled-by-binance-relationship</guid></item><item><title>加密货币溃败加剧，比特币国债损失 620 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/bitcoin-treasury-firms-shed-62-billion-in-deepening-crypto-rout</link><description>比特币本周的下跌给近期加密货币热潮中出现的最雄心勃勃的金融实验之一增添了新的压力：为代表投资者积累数字资产而创建的上市公司。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iurMaImOFPzY/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 04:00:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/bitcoin-treasury-firms-shed-62-billion-in-deepening-crypto-rout</guid></item></channel></rss>